   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>On Tybi 8, has brought Paesis son of Aunes through Ptolas, of the villagers of Karanis, of the 10th (indiction), eighty litrai of chaff, 80 litrai. I, Sokras, have signed.</ab>
         </div>
